CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, December 8, 1962, pg. 18 reads: "Making Presentation - Mrs. Marion E.Bryant (third from left), first vice president of the National Association of Business and Professional Women, Inc., presents a gift from the Pittsburgh club of the NBPA to Mrs. Florence Ball Jones (third from right) at the 40th anniversary celebration of the local group last Sunday. Mrs. Jones is a charter member of the Pittsburgh club.  Left to right: Mmes Betty Moore, Mary Burwell, Daisy E. Lampkin, Lenore Rainey, president; Cora B. Jones and Alma A. Polk. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: National Association of Business and Professional Women, Inc. members Marion E. Bryant, handing gift to Florence Ball Jones, while from left: Betty Moore, Mary Burwell, Daisy E. Lampkin, Lenore Rainey, Cora B. Jones, and Alma A. Polk look on, in Bethesda Presbyterian Church for fortieth anniversary celebration
